text: Yulian Georgiev Manev (Bulgarian: Юлиян Георгиев Манев) (born 13 March 1966) is a Bulgarian former footballer who played as a forward. Manev was a prominent member of the Olympik Teteven team during their only season in the A PFG. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:People from Teteven Category:Bulgarian footballers Category:First Professional Football League (Bulgaria) players Category:Second Professional Football League (Bulgaria) players Category:PFC Vidima-Rakovski Sevlievo players Category:FC Botev Vratsa players Category:Association football forwards
